						               													<description>We've all heard about the legends of the sirens, who with their irresistible voices lure the ships of unsuspecting sailors onto the cliffs... But did you know that they all sing in different musical styles? That's because not every sailor is attracted to the same type of music! Duh!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every 100 years, the sirens of the salty sea wake up from their slumber, to organize the Sirenade festival. Siren clans from across the seven oceans send their most famous stars to vie for the prestigious honor of... Well, being the most badass clan!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Sound of Sirens is a racing game with a lot of interaction between the players. Each player leads a clan of sirens, and each clan is represented by a musical genre: Pop, Ballad, Rap, and Rock.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn, you will be playing action cards from your hand in order to be the first to lure your assigned ship onto the cliffs. But many surprises await along the way&amp;hellip; Do you have what it takes to become a legendary siren?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
